title: WSU building a truly statewide medical school with new dean (Washington State University Spokane)
text: ( Source : Washington State University Spokane ) PULLMAN, Wash . - Dr. John Tomkowiak hit the ground running as he began to assume his duties as inaugural dean of the Washington State University Elson S. Floyd College of Medicine last week.
